Package net.commotionwireless.olsrinfo.datatypes

Provides the classes for the Jackson JSON parser to fill using the data parsed from the JSON data dump from olsrd's jsoninfo plugin.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AddressNetmask An address/netmask pair for specifying networks.
Config The complete startup configuration of olsrd Written as part of the Commotion Wireless project
Gateway A gateway that olsrd is aware of.
HNA A Host and Network Association (HNA) between the current mesh network and another network that is accessible via a given node in the mesh.
Interface A network interface from the list of interfaces that olsrd is aware of at runtime.
Link A mesh link between two nodes in the mesh.
LinkQualityMultiplier A multiplier for a given route to affect its link quality metric.
MID A network interface used in MID (Multiple Interface Declaration) setups.
MIDAlias An alias address for a network interface used in MID (Multiple Interface Declaration) setups.
Neighbor A class representing a first-hop neighbor on the mesh.
Node A node in the whole mesh topology view.
OlsrDataDump A class representing the complete dump of information from olsrd's jsoninfo plugin.
Plugin A class representing an olsrd plugin that was loaded at start time.
Route A class representing a mesh route for a given node.
 

Package net.commotionwireless.olsrinfo.datatypes Description

Provides the classes for the Jackson JSON parser to fill using the data parsed from the JSON data dump from olsrd's jsoninfo plugin. Written as part of the Commotion Wireless project
